params.markdown:
[**Proofpoint ITM**](/app/integrations/detail/proofpoint_itm/overview)

**Report Overview**

This dashboard provides a comprehensive overview of report events, encompassing various metrics such as reports categorized by severity, user activity highlighting the top ten users, rule analysis detailing the top ten rules by category and name, temporal distribution of reports over time, host information showcasing the top ten hosts by name and IP address, site access data presenting the top ten accessed sites along with their URLs, application usage statistics summarizing reports by application names, domain analysis featuring reports by domain names, and operating system metrics summarizing reports by OS.
